---
layout: base.liquid
---
{% comment %}
  Page layout — renders Bookshop blocks defined in frontmatter `blocks:` array.
  Each block is an object with at minimum `_bookshop_name` set to a component
  under component-library/components/<name>/. The block is passed in whole as
  a `block` local so components can `block.<field>` their props.

  If a page has no blocks, the markdown body content is rendered instead
  (used for stub/landing pages during the migration).
{% endcomment %}
{% if blocks %}
  {% for block in blocks %}
    {% bookshop {{block._bookshop_name}} block: block %}
  {% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{{ content }}
